Eventually she finds some eggs in the barn but much to the children's surprise and delight, when one of the eggs cracks open, a sweet little tortoise peeps out!

description: "Lighting up the farm for a big 'festive' celebration Lots of lights around the farm and decorations from different cultures"

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Unica

She loves the slow-paced lessons in discipline and control, but Clarence just wants to have fun and kick butt! Can Mary convince Clarence to stick with the class, earn his belt and have some fun with her?

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Party Popper
description: Apple and Onion's party plans are interrupted by a grumpy guest.

title: The Christmas Parade
description: Mei, Ella, Rishi get the farm decorated for the holidayss and do various christmassy activities

title: Fragments

description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Revienta Fiestas
description: Los planes de la fiesta de Manzana y Cebollín son interrumpidos por un invitado malhumorado.

description: Cuando Craig decide dejar una luciérnaga dentro de un frasco, termina interfiriendo con el delicado equilibrio del verano.

title: Bad Morning
description: When Uncle Grandpa wakes up on the wrong side of the bed, he changes into a grumpy grump and it's up to the rest of the gang to reverse his bad day.

title: I Am Okino
description: Inside one of the game zones, a Samurai named Okino faces a crisis of faith when he repeatedly fails to lead a series of Masters to victory, causing him to lose all hope, until some familiar ninja arrive.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Yo Soy Okino
description: Dentro de una de las zonas de juego, un Samurai llamado Okino se enfrenta a una crisis de fe cuando no logra que los Maestros obtengan la victoria.

description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Rock Show
description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

title: Bichos
description: Cuando Unikitty y la banda descubren un bicho asqueroso en el castillo, están desesperados por deshacerse de él para siempre, pero Unikitty se niega a permitir que lo aplasten, no importa qué tan asqueroso o peligroso parezca. ¿Qué tipo de red está tejiendo Unikitty para sus amigos?

title: Future Pizza
description: When Uncle Grandpa travels back through time with a warning that Pizza Steve will do something to offend him in the next five minutes, Pizza Steve begins to obsess over what he could possibly do to offend Uncle Grandpa.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Steam Fight at the OK Corral
description: When Kevin convinces Steam Smythe to adopt a modern approach in fighting Ben, our young hero must resort to old-fashioned thinking to save the day.

title: The Cursed Word
description: Craig uncovers an ancient Creek Curse.

title: Panda's Family
description: While exploring a lantern festival, the Bears encounter Panda's long-lost family.

title: R & Arr
description: It's Lazy Sunday, and Unikitty and Puppycorn are having such an amazing time hanging out on the couch, they never want to move! Richard insists they have chores to do, but they're unwilling to let Lazy Sunday end. The two go to ridiculous lengths to never leave the comfort of their sofa, rowing it across the castle and like a ship and conscripting their friends to abandon their chores and join Lazy Sunday… no matter how dangerous and impossible it might become!

title: Monstra-City/Shut the Pup Up
description: Monstra-city: When all the monsters move from Monster Isle to Townsville, it's up to the Girls to keep the peace./Shut the Pup Up: When the Talking Dog witnesses a crime, he moves in with the girls for protection. But the girls soon realize this chatterbox dog is less than the perfect pet.

title: The Powerpuff Girls: A Documentary/Girls Gone Mild
description: The Powerpuff Girls a Documentary: A film student attempts to do a documentary on the Powerpuff Girls and learns catching these superheroes at rest is harder than he thought./Girls Gone Mild: When Parents Against Powerpuffs tell the girls that their superheroics are becoming too imitable, the girls must hold back on fighting crime.

title: Craiggy & the Slime Factory
description: Craig and his friends get the first ever tour of the Slime Kids Slime Factory.

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: K-9: Space Puppy
description: Marvin the Martian hires The Looney Builders to build a doghouse on Mars for his puppy, K-9. Daffy soon bonds with K-9 and comes up with a plan to prolong their playtime.

title: The Castle
description: When Mom is away "anything goes" and Dad's lack of rules soon attracts unwelcome houseguests.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Sin Cebollin
description: Manzana trata de sobrevivir un fin de semana solo mientras cuida la planta de Cebollín.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Loose Change
description: Sylvester is upset when Granny paints the bedroom but he learns the importance of change.

title: Spider Sense
description: When a monster ruins their relaxing vacation, the Girls run into a familiar face.

title: Glove Glove Me Do
description: Owen's newly found gloves make him great at everything. But this greatness comes at a high price.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Awesome Brawlers Training  Camp
description: The Awesome Brawlers head to a training facility owned by Kasami International to prepare for the Bakugan Battle League - Los Volmos. But once the gang figures out they will all be competing against each other for the same title, the "team building" retreat doesn't quite go as planned./Agit turns up at the Kasami training facility and fits right in with the Awesome brawlers. This is a lifestyle that he can get used to, but it becomes apparent Agit is torn between a life as a phantom thief and life as a brawler.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: Sad Sax
description: Mordecai wants to get back together with C.J.

title: The Tooth About Zombies
description: When Gwen's favorite event, the Zombie March, falls on the same day as Noah's nightmare event, dental hygienist check up day, Gwen and Noah find a way to help each other out.

title: Garbage Truck
description: Blippi and TABBS shrink down and fly into a garbage truck where they meet Horace, a singing and dancing fly, who shows them what he loves to eat--garbage!

title: Computer Vampire

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Goodbye, Ghost-Scaring Machine
description: Percy announces he's giving up his Ghost Scaring Machine - he's too old for it now. It soon becomes clear that the machine is good for more than just "scaring ghosts."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Truth
description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan

title: Noticias Unikitty
description: Estás viendo el programa de noticias del Unireino Super Good Morning Time Action Information Show, un programa de noticias variadas realizado (mal) por Unikitty y la banda: Hawkodile se encarga del clima, Puppycorn habla deportes, a pesar de no saber ninguna de las reglas, la Dra. Fox tiene un divertido segmento de cocina científica que sale mal, y Richard quiere que el programa deje de emitirse. Unikitty tiene un reportaje contundente y una gran primicia después de la pausa, isi el estudio sobrevive tanto tiempo!

title: Level Thirteen

title: Biggest Dino
description: Blippi wonders what was the biggest dinosaur?

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Soy Mi Monstruo

title: Jake the Dad
description: Jake's a daddy, but being a father and keeping his rainicorn pups from killing themselves or each other is a lot harder than he imagined.

title: Diente de Zombi
description: Cuando el evento favorito de Gwen, el Desfile de los Zombies, cae el mismo día que el día de pesadilla de Beth, la revisión con el dentista, las dos chicas encuentran un modo de ayudarse entre sí.

title: Superstar Rockin' Jay

description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: Rage Rover/To Hive and to Hold/Battle Stations
description: Marvin the Martian proves no match for NASA's Mars Rover. Taz learns about bees… the hard way. Porky and Daffy can't agree on a radio station.

title: Many Happy Returns
description: Gwen and Kevin pay Ben a surprise visit, but does Kevin's strange behavior have anything to do with an angry Tetramand princess, or her father's fleet of warships prepared to attack the Earth?

title: Gwen 10
description: Gwen gets her hands on the Omnitrix and all its powers and now Ben has to take a backseat as Gwen 10 battles Vilgax for control of the device.

title: The Mysterious Revenger/Wynton vs. Lia
description: The Mysterious Revenger: It's the quarter finals of the Bakugan Battle League, the top eight brawlers are set to face off! In this round, Dan will face off against the Bakugan rocker - Revenger! These two brawlers give it their all in this icy cold clash!/Wynton Vs. Lia: The quarter finals continue, and it's the first Awesome Brawler vs. Awesome Brawler matches of the Bakugan Battle League tournament. In this round, it's Wynton vs. Lia and Shun vs. Lightning.

title: Big Trouble Little Babies
description: When they realize they're too small for the rides at an amusement park, the Bears use a magic potion to get bigger.

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: El chico del 3030
description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Malefactor
description: Khyber and his dog attacks Ben and Rook while they're at the "Olde Bellwood Days" festival, but does the hunter have other plans? (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Hypnotick.)

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Big Tick
description: A giant alien tick that sucks planets dry, lands on Earth with the sole purpose of destroying the planet and only a new alien hero can stop it.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: No Me Agradas
description: La batalla de Ben y Gwen contra Kevin 11 en las redes sociales se convierte rápidamente en una guerra sin cuartel en la vida real.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Una Idea Huev-Xtremadamente Mala
description: Esperando "iluminar su día", Izzy y Owen decoran la silla huevo de Gwe. Pero cuando termina en un museo regentado por pollos rabiosos, deben rescatarla antes de que Gwen destruya la guardería en un berrinche de inusitada oscuridad.

title: Whiskers
description: Blippi wonders why do cats have whiskers?

title: Buscando a Jessica
description: Jessica se adentra en un Arroyo desconocido, iy Craig debe encontrarla antes de que su madre se dé cuenta!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: The Knights
description: Gumball and Tobias compete for Penny's affection by putting on the lamest duel in history.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Jay Estrella del Rock
description: Dentro de Primer Imperio, los ninjas se encuentran en un territorio desconocido e intentan encontrar a Jay y escapar de los Visores Rojos de Unagami.

title: An Egg-stremely Bad Idea
description: Hoping to 'brighten her day', Izzy and Owen pimp out Gwen's egg chair. But when it ends up in a museum run by angry chickens, they must retrieve it before Gwen destroys the daycare in a temper tantrum of unspeakable darkness.

title: I Don't Like You
description: Ben and Gwen's social media battle with Kevin 11 quickly escalates into an all-out war in real life.

title: Pelea de Vapor en el Corral
Unikitty News!
description: You're watching the Unikingdom News Show Super Good Morning Time Program Action Information Show, a variety news program put on (badly) by Unikitty and the gang: Hawkodile does the weather, Puppycorn does sports despite knowing none of the rules, Dr. Fox puts on a fun science-y cooking segment that goes awry, and Richard wants this to stop. Unikitty's got some hard hitting reporting and a big scoop after the break, if the studio survives that long!

title: The Authority
description: Granny JoJo's overprotective behavior puts the Wattersons in danger...from themselves.

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: You Remind Me of Someone
description: Ben and Gwen look for the infamous Bojamboo (the Bigfoot of the South) and discover that it's actually the Forgeti, at the same time as Kevin 11, but when Ben and Kevin are blasted with the Forgeti's forgetfulness mist, they reverse roles and it's up to Gwen and Max to restore them back to normal.

title: Kung Fu Master/A Battle of Popularity
description: Kung Fu Master: Dan's first match-up of the Bakugan battle league is the Chinese Champion Brawler: Zhao. His opponent is a deeply focused, and serious brawler, who uses Kung Fu techniques in battle. It's going to take all Dan and Drago's focus and strength to get through this opponent!/A Battle of Popularity: Shun and Wynton's first match-ups in the Bakugan battle league take place at the same time. Even though they're not battling each other, Wynton can't help getting a little competitive with Shun, bragging that he can get the crowd cheering louder than Shun. The brawls quickly turn into a popularity contest, instead of a Bakugan battle!

title: That's What's Up
description: Beast Boy heads back east to visit his family, the Doom Patrol, and they decide to throw a clambake to celebrate.

title: Dinner Apart-y
description: Unikitty and Puppycorn are invited to Master Frown and Brock's apartment for a dinner party. But the two roommates are butting heads, and are anything but on the same page. Can Unikitty help Brock and Master Frown get back in harmony before the dinner party is ruined? Will Puppycorn figure out which door is the bathroom?

title: Take Your Kids to Dooms Day
description: The Girls spend the day with the Professor at his boring office, only to find that the office comes with a terrible secret.

title: License to Punch
description: Hawkodile's caught by the Action Police for bodyguarding without an Action License. He's can't protect the kingdom or do anything rad until he does, but the test at the DMV (The Department of Mayhem and Violence) is for nerds! Forced to retire his gloves, Hawkodile struggles to live a life without punching, so Unikitty vows to help her friend contain his urge to be action-y and study for the test. But there's more to the test than meets the eye.

title: Jessica's Trail
description: Jessica wanders into an unfamiliar creek, leaving Craig to find her before his Mom notices!

title: The Bakugan Battle League Begins/Riot vs. Ajit
description: The Bakugan Battle League Begins: The qualifying rounds for the Bakugan Battle league are taking place all around Los Volmos. The Awesome Brawlers all make it through into the tournament without a hitch, that is all but Dan. Dan faces an old rival in Trey, who's back with a few tricks up his sleeve./Riot vs. Ajit: The Bakugan battle league is finally here and 16 brawlers have qualified to enter including all the Awesome Brawlers. The first round will feature a brawl between China Riot and the golden Bakugan brawler, Agit!

title: Licencia para Golpear
description: A Hawkodile lo atrapa la policía de acción por trabajar como guardaespaldas sin licencia de acción. No puede proteger el reino ni hacer nada radical hasta tener la licencia, ipero la prueba en el Departamento de Caos y Violencia es para los nerds! Obligado a quitarse los guantes, Hawkodile lucha por vivir una vida sin golpes, por lo que Unikitty promete ayudar a su amigo a contener su impulso de entrar en acción y a estudiar para la prueba. Pero la prueba consiste en algo más de lo que parece.

title: Buggin' Out
description: When Unikitty and the gang discover a gross bug in the castle, they desperately want it gone for good, but Unikitty refuses to allow them to squish it, no matter how icky or dangerous looking it is. What sort of web is Unikitty weaving for her friends?

title: Pouting Match
description: Lola tries pouting to get what she wants, and soon all the babies are doing it.

title: Terror Tales of the Park IV
description: The park guys try to keep Muscle Man awake with scary stories on a long drive so that they can meet his mom.

title: Stop That Ducky!
description: After snagging an ultra-fuel-cell upgrade, Penguin's Ducky Boat suddenly becomes the fastest vehicle in Gotham. Confident leader Bam must rally the Batwheels to stop the turbo-Ducky!

title: Rose's Scabbard
description: Steven joins Pearl on a special mission to a place that belonged to Rose-Quartz.

title: Hurricane Dilliss
description: Things in the Wendle household are turned upside down when Mary's mom Dyllis comes to visit, butting her way into every corner of Clarence, Mary and Chad's life.

title: Snake Babies
description: Charlie adopts baby snakes despite the Bears thinking he's not ready for parenthood.

title: Manzana es Bajito
description: Manzana tiene que ser alto para poder enamorarse.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: El Menti-Ranosaurio
description: Owen finge ser el dinosaurio mascota de Izzy después de hacerle creer que lo sacó del patio de la escuela.

title: Brobots
description: Cyborg comes to visit Beast Boy, but once Cyborg realizes how much he and Robotman have in common, they become inseparable.

title: The Future
description: Steven is finally ready to move on.

title: Framed
description: Kevin 11 is back and out for revenge. And with the ability to shape-shift into several of Ben's alien heroes, he's been framing Ben for his crimes.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Rumbo al Planeta Madre
description: Steven acude a las Diamantes para pedirles consejos sobre cómo controlar sus nuevos poderes.

title: Story for Steven
description: Greg tells Steven the full story of how he met Rose-Quartz.

title: Sandcastle
description: Blippi and TABBS go to the beach, where they meet Crabby the Crab! A local expert on sandcastles, Crabby teaches them how to build a castle that can't get washed away!

title: Robo-Maestra
description: Cuando una maestra suplente reemplaza a Chef, Duncan cree que será el mejor día de la historia. Se equivoca.

title: More Uncle Grandpa Shorts
description: Series of shorts starring everyone's favorite uncle and grandpa!

title: Rigby's Graduation Day Special
description: Rigby has to give a speech at his high school graduation. The speech will be broadcast live on a TV show called Inspire America, and Rigby wants to make it memorable.

title: Secret Origin of the Batwheels
description: When Batman, Robin, and Batgirl are all captured, the Batcomputer brings the Bat-Vehicles to life. Now the newly-minted Batwheels must defend the Batcave and face off with the Legion of Zoom… all without Batman's help!

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: The Titans Show
description: The Titans try to get off the desert island but soon realize everything is not as it seems.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: A Rusty Rescue
description: When Thomas throws away Diesel's favorite oil can thinking it's trash, he makes a promise to get it back and learns it's better not to touch things that aren't yours.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple wants to experience love.

title: Outbreak
description: When Dr. Psychobos steals a part out of the Omnitrix, causing chaotic side effects, it's up to Ben, Rook, and a small team of Plumbers get everything back to normal. (Introducing new Ben alien Kickin' Hawk, temp Ben alien Walkatrout, Upchuck Rook.)

title: I Am My Mom
description: Steven struggles to fix his mistakes.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Chinese New Year
description: The farm is decorated for Chinese New Year. A party is taking place!

title: Adrenalandia Junior
description: El equipo de Tennyson visita la versión segura de Adrenalandia, conocida como "Adrenalandia Jr", y allí terminan enfrentándose a un Kevin 11 amargado y decidido a destruir la diversión segura de todos los demás.

title: Face Your Fears
description: Apple and Onion must face their fears if they are to save French Fry from their bad advice.

title: More Cowbell
description: Thomas is elated when he finds a cowbell on the side of the tracks, until his friends start hogging it.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: Que Rima Con Omnitrix?
description: En un recital de lectura de poesía, Charmcaster lee poemas de Kevin y les causa problemas mágicos a Ben y Gwen cuando produce intercambios mentales que dejan a todos confundidos acerca de quién pelea contra quién.

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: A Tale of Two Ice Bears
description: The Bears accidentally clone Ice Bear and Ice Bear has a hard time adjusting.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Grudge Match
description: Ben and Kevin 11 are beamed up to a space ship where must learn to battle together in order to bring down a vicious alien fight promoter.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Imagine That
description: The Girls have to battle Him after he causes Bubbles' imagination to run wild.

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: Todo Esta Bien
description: Steven insiste en que todo está bien.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Easter Bunny Hop
description: Bunny Bun-Buns is going to do some baking but he needs some help collecting the ingredients. He hops around the farm with Ella and Rishi to collect some milk from Carlos, some eggs from Mama Duck and a carrot from the vegetable patch. Now they can bake his favourite thing - a carrot cake!

title: The Outside
description: The family goes to visit Richard's Dad. Based on his basic living standards and extended absence from Richard's life, they assume Frankie must have done a stretch in the slammer. When Frankie comes to stay with the Wattersons, they decide the way to make him comfortable is to make him uncomfortable and turn their house into a prison.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Cena Festiva
description: Unikitty y Puppycorn están invitados al apartamento de Master Frown y Brock para una cena. Pero los dos compañeros de casa no logran ponerse de acuerdo absolutamente en nada. ¿Puede Unikitty ayudar a Brock y al Master Frown a volver a estar en armonía antes de que la cena sea un desastre? ¿Y descubrirá Puppycorn cuál es la puerta del baño?

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Fragmentos
description: Steven se dirige al bosque para entrenarse con un poderoso mentor.

title: Wise Quacker
description: Melissa gets laughs doing hurtful impressions of the other kids, but she takes the jokes too far.

title: Viewer Special
description: Uncle Grandpa announces the winner of a contest to draw the latest episode of Uncle Grandpa.  Too bad the winner is a metalhead who torments the gang with his strange doodles.

title: Dinner Party
description: When Clarence's mom takes Clarence to a stuffy dinner party, Clarence embarks on a quest for fun wherever it can be found.

title: A Regular Epic Final Battle Part 1
description: An epic final battle begins.

title: Lying Around the House/Bubble Boy
description: Lying Around The House: The girls tell little white lies that turn into a big, bad problem./Bubble Boy: Realizing that the only way to beat the Rowdyruff Boys is to join them, Bubbles takes Boomer's place in this rough-and-tumble band of boys.

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Spiderweb
description: A gorgeous spider web in the park has Blippi wondering "How do spiders make their webs?" He sets off to find the answer! A very talented spider explains the artistic process and Blippi is surprised by the masterful picture that ends up in the spiders' web!

title: Silly Hat Catastrophe!/Zee In A Bottle
description: Lloyd is selling silly hats at the factory, but when the hat machine malfunctions it starts raining silly hats on Pretty Big City!/Zee makes a giant rocket ship in a bottle, but things take a turn when he gets stuck inside!

title: Adrenaland Jr.
description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

title: Jakesuit
description: Jake is sick and tired of Finn using his body as a suit of armor so he convinces Finn to trade places to show him how much it really stinks.

title: Waffle Cones for Whiffles
description: The Whiffles are too hot and tired to work because their daily treat, colorful ice in Waffles Cones delivered by the whimsical "Icelings," hasn't arrived - the Icelings have mysteriously disappeared. As the Care Bears search for them, Share volunteers to make the treats. It's much more than she can handle but she's determined to go-it-alone and not ask for help. Things get out of hand and Share ends up snared in Bluster's trap with the Icelings, who help her to realize that we get more done when we work together.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Gone Fishin'
description: When their fishing trip in Undertown takes a bizarre twist, Ben, Rook, and Grandpa Max, begin their search for a ship-bottling alien pirate who has captured Magister Patelliday. (Introducing Capt. Cork.)

title: Monkey Love
description: When Blossom makes a bad call, she becomes afraid to try again.

title: Power-Noia
description: The girls have become paralyzed by their greatest fears. Who could be behind such an evil trick?

title: Me Recuerdas a Alguien
description: Ben y Gwen buscan al tristemente célebre Bojamboo (el Pie Grande del Sur) y descubren que en realidad se trata del Olvideti.

title: Onionless
description: Onion needs to leave town so Apple has to survive the weekend alone while taking care of Onion's beloved plant.

title: Dumped at the Altar
description: The guys have to get Muscle Man married.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Magnus P.I.
description: There's a been a string of thefts and each one has involved a Bakugan. The AAAnimus security force have decided the only brawler who could be responsible is: Magnus. The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Domingo de Flojos
description: Es domingo de pereza, iy Unikitty y Puppycorn la están pasando tan bien en el sofá que no quieren moverse nunca! Richard insiste en que tienen tareas por hacer, pero ellos no están dispuestos a dejar que termine el domingo de pereza. Los dos hacen todo lo posible para no salir nunca de la comodidad de su sofá, remando por el castillo como si estuvieran en un barco y reclutando a sus amigos para que abandonen sus tareas y se unan al domingo de pereza, isin importar qué tan peligroso e imposible puede llegar a ser!
